text: Josef Kos (born 1892, date of death unknown) was a Czech gymnast. He competed in four events at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1892 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Czech male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Czechoslovakia Category:Gymnasts at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Hradec Králové
